Are you Google? Because you have everything I'm searching for.
Are you a magician? Because you make everyone else disappear.
Are you a campfire? Because you’re hot and I want s’more.
Are you a time traveler? Because I see you in my future.
Are you a bank loan? Because you got my interest.
Are you my phone charger? Because I can’t live without you.
Are you a keyboard? Because you’re just my type.
Are you a comet? Because you light up my world.
Are you my morning coffee? Because you brighten my day.
